vote.title: An ordinance abandoning a portion of Killion Drive to Dallas Independent School District, the abutting owner, containing approximately 818 square feet of land, located near the intersection of Killion and Gooding Drives; and authorizing the quitclaim - Revenue: General Fund $12,066.00, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
